---

<!-- CV Page -->
<Portfolio
  pageTitle="Hire Me"
  pageUrl="/hire-me"
  header="Wanna work with me? Read on."
  pageDescription="Here's how you can hire me for your next project. I'm available for freelance work, contract work, and full-time employment. I'm also open to collaborations and partnerships. Let's talk!"
>
  <article class="rounded-lg border-2 border-xephas-navy p-6 space-y-4">
    <LinkH2 text="My Cover Letter" align="text-center" , id="cover-letter" />
    <p id="#" class="mt-2 font-bold text-xs text-xephas-blue italic text-center">
      Last Updated: 28th May, 2024
    </p>

    <p class="mt-4">Greetings to you,</p>
    <p>
      I am <strong>Mugisa Brian (Cephas)</strong>, a Ugandan Software Engineer
      with over three years of ultimate experience in Cross-Platform App
      Development with Flutter and an astounding passion for Graphics and UI/UX
      Design. My purpose is to design and develop experiences that improve
      people's lives.
    </p>

    <p>
      <strong
        >I am writing to express my strong interest in the Senior Flutter
        Developer position at your company.</strong
