      contribute to your dynamic team. I am particularly drawn to your mission of
      creating digital products that humanize technology and enhance the day-to-day
      lives of users.
    </p>

    <!-- why me -->
    <LinkH2 text="Why Me?" , id="why-me" />
    <div>
      <!-- flutter expertise -->
      <LinkH3 text="Flutter Expertise" bullet="a)" />
      <p>
        My expertise in <InlineLink
          target="_blank"
          ,
          href="https://flutter.dev/"
          ,
          text="Flutter"
        /> development is best demonstrated through my open-source and personal projects
        below:
      </p>
      <!-- projects -->
      <div class="ml-8 mt-2 space-y-2">
        <li>
          <InlineLink
            target="_blank"
            ,
            href="https://calcut.page.link/visit"
            ,
            text="Calcut | The Cut-Off Points Companion"
          /> (with over 6,500 users)
        </li>
        <li>
          <InlineLink
            target="_blank"
            ,
            href="https://cupertino.page.link/icons"
            ,
            text="Cupertino Icons Gallery"
          /> A home to over 1,330 Cupertino Icons used in Flutter (Open Source with
          16 GitHub Stars) used by over 4,900 Flutter Developers around the World.
        </li>
        <li>
          <InlineLink
            target="_blank"
            ,
            href="https://draaaft.page.link/visit"
            ,
            text="Draaaft"
          />
          (A graphics design portfolio and ordering app) with over 400 users.
        </li>
        <li>
          <InlineLink
            target="_blank"
            ,
            href="https://kalyacourtshotel.web.app/"
            ,
            text="Kalya Courts Hotel Management System"
          />
        </li>
        <li>
          <InlineLink
            target="_blank"
            ,
            href="https://shoplix.web.app/"
            ,
            text="Shoplix | Online Food Shop"
          />
        </li>
        <li>
          <InlineLink
            target="_blank"
            ,
            href="https://fluttercommdashboard.web.app/"
            ,
            text="Flutter Community Dashboard App"
          />| Built during my Participation In Dart Google Summer Of Code (Open
          Source).
        </li>
        <li>
          <InlineLink
            target="_blank"
            ,
            href="https://thumbsapp.page.link/test"
            ,
            text="Thumbs App"
          /> | A video Streaming Platform.
        </li>
        <li>
          STTS Mobile App for Seed Tracing and Tracking, <em
            >developed during my blended internship (Remote + Physical) from
            June to September 2023, at Eight Tech Consults Ltd.</em
          >
        </li>
      </div>

      <!--  -->
      <p class="mt-4">
        These applications reflect my commitment to crafting functional and
        user-friendly Flutter experiences.
      </p>

      <!-- Community -->
      <LinkH3 text="Developer Community Contributions" bullet="b)" />
      <p>
        I am actively involved in the Ugandan Developer (Flutter) Community
        since 2022, contributing as a <strong
          >Speaker and Facilitator (Trainer)</strong
        > in prominent events such as <strong
          >Flutter Forward Kampala 2023</strong
        > and <strong>DroidCon Uganda 2023</strong>. Additionally, I've
        conducted training sessions at events like the
        <strong>Flutter Series Training Bootcamp</strong>, where I mentored over
        100 student developers in 2022 and 2023 at the Google Developer Students
        Club, Makerere University. Moreover, I've participated in online
        sessions, including a <strong
          >Twitter Space hosted by Eight Tech Institute to discuss the Flutter
          developer landscape in Uganda</strong
        >, February 2024, and Speaking at the <strong
          >Flutter Kampala Meetup</strong
        > and <strong>IWD (International Women's Day) Mbarara</strong> in March 2024.
        <InlineLink
          href="/community"
          text="Learn more about my community contributions."
        />
      </p>

