      <LinkH3 text="Firebase Integration" bullet="c)" />
      <p>
        I possess extensive experience integrating Google's <InlineLink
          target="_blank"
          ,
          href="https://firebase.google.com/"
          ,
          text="Firebase"
        /> services and <InlineLink
          target="_blank"
          ,
          href="https://cloud.google.com/"
          ,
          text="Google Cloud"
        /> functionalities. This is best demonstrated by the secure user authentication
        and seamless data management across all applications in my <InlineLink
          target="_blank"
          ,
          href="#flutter-expertise"
          ,
          text="portfolio."
        />
      </p>

      <!-- coding style -->
      <LinkH3 text="Clean Coding Style" bullet="d)" />
      <p>
        My Flutter coding style emphasizes clean, reusable, and efficient code.
        I have created a <InlineLink
          target="_blank"
          ,
          href="https://github.com/capps096github/xephas_app"
          ,
          text="Flutter App Code Generator"
        /> that serves as the foundation for setting up <strong
          >New Flutter applications.</strong
        > This tool further showcases my dedication to maintaining high coding standards
        and streamlining the development process.
      </p>

      <!-- state management -->
      <LinkH3 text="State Management Expertise" bullet="e)" />
      <p>
        In Flutter development, I leverage advanced state management techniques
        using <InlineLink
          target="_blank"
          ,
          href="https://pub.dev/packages/flutter_riverpod"
          ,
          text="Riverpod"
        /> and <InlineLink
          target="_blank"
          ,
          href="https://pub.dev/packages/provider"
          ,
          text="Provider"
        />
        to create scalable, efficient, and maintainable applications. My commitment
        to this efficient state management architecture is best reflected in projects
        like <InlineLink
          target="_blank"
          ,
          href="https://calcut.page.link/visit"
          ,
          text="Calcut"
        />
        where robust state management plays a crucial role in delivering seamless
        user experiences.
      </p>
      <!-- remote work -->
      <LinkH3 text="Remote Work Experience" bullet="f)" />
      <p>
        As a Remote Software Engineer, I am adept at managing projects
        independently while staying connected with my team. Despite the
        geographical distance, I prioritize clear communication and
        collaborative teamwork, ensuring that project objectives are met
        effectively.
      </p>

      <!-- beyond flutter -->
      <LinkH3
